\c 38
\s Aritari yekupisira, nedhishi, nechivanze
\p
\v 1 Zvino wakaita aritari yechipo chinopiswa nematanda emuakasia\x + 27.7; 27.1-8.\x*; kureba kwayo mbimbi shanu, neupamhi hwayo mbimbi shanu, nhivi ina dzakaenzana, nekukwirira kwayo mbimbi nhatu.
\v 2 Wakaitawo nyanga dzayo pamakona ayo mana; nyanga dzayo dzaibva pairi; ndokuiputira nendarira.
\v 3 Wakaitawo midziyo yose yearitari, hari, nefoshoro, nendiro dzekusasa, zvibaiso zvenyama, nemakango epamoto; midziyo yayo yose akaiita nendarira.
\v 4 Akaitirawo aritari sefa yendarira, basa remumbure, pasi pemucheto wayo, kubva pazasi kusvika pakati payo.
\v 5 Zvino wakaumbira nekunyungudusa zvindori zvina kumicheto mina yesefa yendarira, nzvimbo dzezvibatiso.
\v 6 Wakaitawo zvibatiso zvematanda emuakasia ndokuzviputira nendarira.
\v 7 Zvino wakaisa zvibatiso muzvindori panhivi dzearitari kuitakura nazvo; akaita ive mhango nemapuranga.
\p
\v 8 Akaitawo dhishi rendarira, negumbo raro rendarira\x + 30.18.\x*, nezvionioni zvevakadzi vanoungana vaiungana pamukova wetende rekusangana.
\p
\v 9 Wakaitawo chivanze; kurutivi rwechamhembe kwakatarisa kuchamhembe kwaiva kune zviremberedzwa zvechivanze\x + 27.20; 27.9-19.\x* zvemucheka wakaisvonaka wakarukwa, mbimbi zana;
\v 10 mbiru dzayo \add dzaiva\add* makumi maviri, nezvigadziko zvadzo makumi maviri zvendarira; zvikorekedzo zvembiru nezvisungo zvadzo \add zvaiva\add* zvesirivha.
\v 11 Zvino kurutivi rwemaodzanyemba \add kwaiva ne\add*makubhiti zana\x + 27.11.\x*, mbiru dzayo makumi maviri, nezvigadziko zvadzo zvendarira makumi maviri; zvikorekedzo zvembiru nezvisungo zvadzo \add zvaiva\add* zvesirivha.
\v 12 Zvino kurutivi rwemavirazuva \add kwaiva\add* \add ne\add*zviremberedzwa \add zve\add*mbimbi makumi mashanu, mbiru dzazvo gumi, nezvigadziko zvadzo gumi; zvikorekedzo zvembiru nezvisungo zvadzo \add zvaiva zve\add*sirivha.
\v 13 Zvino kurutivi rwemabvazuva kwakatarisa kumabvazuva \add kwaiva ne\add*mbimbi makumi mashanu.
\v 14 Zviremberedzwa zvedivi \add rimwe zvaiva\add* mbimbi gumi neshanu, mbiru dzazvo nhatu, nezvigadziko zvadzo zvitatu.
\v 15 Nekurumwe rutivi rwesuwo rechivanze apa neuko \add kwaiva\add* nezviremberedzwa mbimbi gumi neshanu, mbiru dzazvo nhatu, nezvigadziko zvadzo zvitatu.
\v 16 Zviremberedzwa zvose zvechivanze zvaipoteredza \add zvaiva\add* \add zve\add*mucheka wakaisvonaka wakarukwa.
\v 17 Nezvigadziko zvembiru \add zvaiva\add* ndarira, zvikorekedzo zvembiru nezvisungo zvadzo \add zvaiva\add* sirivha; nechifukidzo chemisoro yayo \add chaiva\add* sirivha; nembiru dzose dzechivanze dzaiva dzakasunganidzwa nesirivha.
\v 18 Nechiremberedzwa chesuwo rechivanze chaiva basa remusoni, zveruvara rwedenga, neruvara rwehute, nezvitsvuku, nemucheka wakaisvonaka wakarukwa; kureba kuri mbimbi makumi maviri, nekukwirira paupamhi mbimbi shanu, zvichienderana nezviremberedzwa zvechivanze.
\v 19 Zvino mbiru dzayo \add dzaiva\add* ina, nezvigadziko zvadzo zvendarira zvina; zvikorekedzo zvadzo zviri sirivha, nechifukidzo chemisoro yadzo nezvisungo zvadzo zviri sirivha.
\v 20 Nehoko dzose dzetabhenakeri nedzechivanze dzakapoteredza \add dzaiva\add* ndarira.
\s Fuma yose yakavakiswa tabhenakeri nayo
\p
\v 21 Ndihwo uwandu hwezvinhu zvetabhenakeri, zvetabhenakeri yechipupuriro\x + Num.. 1.50,53; 10.11. Num.. 9.15; 17.7,8; 18.2. 2 Makor. 24.6. Mab. 7.44. 16.34.\x*, zvakaverengwa maererano nekuraira kwaMozisi, basa reVaRevhi neruoko rwaItamari, mwanakomana waAroni mupristi\x + 6.23. 28.1. Num.. 4.28,33.\x*.
\v 22 NaBhezareeri, mwanakomana waUri\x + 31.2,6.\x*, mwanakomana waHuri, werudzi rwaJudha, wakaita zvose Jehovha zvaakaraira Mozisi.
\v 23 Zvino pamwe naye \add paiva\add* naOhoriabhu mwanakomana waAhisamaki, werudzi rwaDhani, mufombori nemubati wakachenjera, nemusoni wezveruvara rwedenga\x + 26.36.\x*, newezveruvara rwehute, newezvitsvuku, nemucheka wakaisvonaka.
\p
\v 24 Goridhe rose raishandiswa pabasa, pabasa rose repaimba tsvene, iro goridhe rezvipo\x + 38.29. 35.22.\x*, raiva matarenda makumi maviri nemapfumbamwe, nemashekeri mazana manomwe nemakumi matatu, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene\x + 38.25,26. 30.13,24. Rev. 5.15. 27.3,25. Num.. 3.47,50. 7.13,19,25,31,37. 18.16.\x*.
\v 25 Nesirivha yaivo vaiva vachiverengwa paungano yaiva matarenda zana, nemashekeri churu chimwe nemazana manomwe nemakumi manomwe nemashanu, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene.
\v 26 Bheka* pamusoro\x + Gen.. 24.22. 30.13,15.\x*, ndiro hafu yeshekeri, zvichienzaniswa neshekeri reimba tsvene, kune umwe neumwe wakadarika kune vakaverengwa, kubva pamakore makumi maviri zvichikwira, vaiva zvuru mazana matanhatu nezvitatu nemazana mashanu nemakumi mashanu\x + Num.. 1.46.\x*.
\v 27 Uye kwaiva nematarenda esirivha zana ekuumbisa nekunyungudusa zvigadziko zvepaimba tsvene nezvigadziko zvevheiri; zvigadziko zana zvematarenda zana, tarenda rechigadziko\x + 26.19,21,25,32.\x*.
\v 28 Ne\add mashekeri\add* churu nemazana manomwe nemakumi manomwe nemashanu wakaitira mbiru zvikorekedzo, akaputira misoro yadzo, nekudziitira zvisungo.
\v 29 Nendarira yechipo \add yaiva\add* matarenda makumi manomwe nemashekeri zvuru zviviri nemazana mana.
\v 30 Nayo wakaita zvigadziko\x + 26.37.\x* zvemukova wetende rekusangana, nearitari yendarira, nesefa yendarira yayaiva nayo\x + 27.2-4.\x*, nemidziyo yose yepaaritari,
\v 31 nezvigadziko zvechivanze chakapoteredza\x + 27.10-12.\x*, nezvigadziko zvesuwo rechivanze\x + 27.16,17.\x*, nehoko dzose dzetabhenakeri\x + 27.19.\x*, nehoko dzose dzechivanze chakapoteredza.